  user-table output).
- **New `scripts/xcesp-login`** — installed to
  `/usr/lib/xcesp/xcesp-login` (off PATH).  Maps the user's
  primary group (xcespg1..xcespg4) to a CliRole and exec's
  xcespcli with `--role` and the system control socket.  Also
  mirrored into `mainsw/scripts/` so CLI upgrades self-refresh
  it via xcesp-activate.
