    on the `sshd-integration` flag; reload sshd when it changes
  - reserved names (root, xcesp, daemon, bin, sys, nobody) are
    never touched
- **xcespserver.ini** — new `MANAGED_USERS_FILE` key in
  `[SERVER]`, default `/var/lib/xcesp/managed-users.state`.
  Commenting it out disables the feature entirely.
