  and Ch04 (DHCPv6 relay) surfaced against the kea-dhcp6-server
  shipping on Fedora 41.  Includes: KEA_* env-var overrides for the
  build-time "supported paths" restrictions; chmod 0750 on the
  control-socket directory; subnet `"interface"` attribute for direct
